<h3 id="grading">Grading</h3>

<p>You‚Äôll be graded on:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Brush creation.</li>
  <li>Brush use.</li>
  <li>Final artwork execution.</li>
  <li>The resolution set as directed.</li>
  <li>Your layers are all named.</li>
  <li>Non-destructive editing.</li>
  <li>Save progressive version in Layer Groups.</li>
  <li>Show progress in <a href="https://helpx.adobe.com/photoshop/how-to/layer-comp-updates.html" title="Adobe's tutorial on Layer Comps in Photohsop." target="_blank">Layer Comps</a>.</li>
</ul>

<h3 id="deliverables">Deliverables</h3>

<ul>
